    <title>Flag state requirements</title>
    <pics>
      <pic preload="X" noFade="X" y="0" x="0">Background1.jpg</pic>
      <pic noFade="X" y="159" x="205">PS0204.swf</pic>
    </pics>
    <sounds>
      <snd>
      </snd>
      <snd>31.mp3</snd>
    </sounds>
    <texts>
      <txt c="X" s="2">
      </txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2">
      </txt>
    </texts>
    <soundTexts>
      <sndTxt>
      </sndTxt>
      <sndTxt>Rules and regulations of the flag state include provisions requiring that all employees shall undergo certain health control procedures prior to serving onboard a vessel. The extent of the control and the specific requirements depend on the position in which the person shall serve. You should make yourselves familiar with the rules and regulation your vessel's flag state require.</sndTxt>
    </soundTexts>
  </page>
